      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1778703079778,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "*IDEA: This is a rotation lock - the password = how many times every rotation made lands on a '0'.\n- Number AFTER 99 = 0\n- Number BEFORE 0 = 99\n\n- *VARS: MIN = 0; MAX = 99; Start = 50; Curr. = Start; NumZeros = 0\n\n- E.g. rotation = 'L68':\n    - Split L/R from rotation = ['L', '68']\n    - direction = rotation[0]\n    - turns = rotation[1]\n    - IFF direction == 'L', THEN:\n        - IFF (Curr. - turns) < MIN, THEN:\n              Curr. = (MAX+1) - (turns - Curr.)\n          ELSE:\n              Curr. = Curr. - turns\n    - IFF direction == 'R', THEN:\n        - IFF (Curr. + turns) > MAX, THEN:\n              Curr. = 0 + (MAX+1 - Curr.)\n          ELSE:\n              Curr. = Curr. + turns\n- IFF Curr. == 0, THEN NumZeros++",
      "fontSize": 16,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "*IDEA: This is a rotation lock - the password = how many times every rotation made lands on a '0'.\n- Number AFTER 99 = 0\n- Number BEFORE 0 = 99\n\n- *VARS: MIN = 0; MAX = 99; Start = 50; Curr. = Start; NumZeros = 0\n\n- E.g. rotation = 'L68':\n    - Split L/R from rotation = ['L', '68']\n    - direction = rotation[0]\n    - turns = rotation[1]\n    - IFF direction == 'L', THEN:\n        - IFF (Curr. - turns) < MIN, THEN:\n              Curr. = (MAX+1) - (turns - Curr.)\n          ELSE:\n              Curr. = Curr. - turns\n    - IFF direction == 'R', THEN:\n        - IFF (Curr. + turns) > MAX, THEN:\n              Curr. = 0 + (MAX+1 - Curr.)\n          ELSE:\n              Curr. = Curr. + turns\n- IFF Curr. == 0, THEN NumZeros++",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    }
